{"title":"HY看小说（黄烨看小说升级版）","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5945","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p style=\"\">HY非常喜欢看小说，每次老师讲完课后他就开始看小说。<br></p><p style=\"\"><span style=\"\"> <span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\"><strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">   这回HY迷上了看网络小说，一上完OI他就上网看小说。</span></em></strong><strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\"></span></em></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"\">这几天HY新发现了n部网络小说，每本书他需要看的时间各不相同，第i部他要看n<sub>i</sub>分钟,n<sub>i</sub>各不相同。</p><p style=\"\">现在，老师讲完课了，HY开始看小说。</p><p style=\"\">他想看k部网络小说，并且他看这k本小说的时间加起来刚刚好是s分钟，请问他有多少种选择方案？</p><p style=\"\">他自己懒得算，于是就找到了编程大牛的你。<br></p><p style=\"\">请你编一个程序帮他解决这个问题吧。</p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\">第1行：n，k，s</p><p style=\"\">第2行~n+1行：n个n<span style=\"\">i</span></p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 102, 110); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, 微软雅黑, 黑体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">方案的个数。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\">3 2 4</p><p style=\"\">1 2 3</p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">1</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\">3&lt;=n&lt;=100000;2&lt;=k&lt;=3;n^k&lt;=<span style=\"font-family: 'Calibri','sans-serif';\">10^12;</span></p><p style=\"\">1&lt;=n<sub>i</sub>&lt;=n;</p><p style=\"\">注：1+3=4与3+1=4是同一种情况。</p><p><br></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}